<div class="dablink">This article is about the Christian denomination.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Shaker_(disambiguation)" title="Shaker (disambiguation)">Shaker (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:352px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Shakers_Dancing.jpg" class="image" title="Shaker dance and worship"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b5/Shakers_Dancing.jpg/350px-Shakers_Dancing.jpg" width="350" height="179" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Shakers_Dancing.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<i>Shaker dance and worship</i></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>The <b>United Society of Believers in Christ’s Second Appearing</b>, known as the <b>Shakers</b>, is a <a href="/wiki/Protestant" title="Protestant" class="mw-redirect">Protestant</a> religious denomination.</p>
